Lustre-LFS version 0.01
========================

This module provides replacements for IO::File
and IO::Handle with integrated 'get_stripe' and 'set_stripe'
support. (Well: Actually this module does not replace the
IO::* modules, it just inherits from them :-) )

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

